                          professional tone keep message direct polite concrete free jokes filler unsupported claims                                                                      Professional tone                                               Keep the message direct, polite, concrete, and free of jokes, filler, or unsupported claims.                                                                                                    formal memo subject line one-sentence purpose short body paragraphs explicit next action                                                                        Formal memo                                                     Use a subject line, one-sentence purpose, short body paragraphs, and an explicit next action.                                                                                                   meeting notes capture decisions owners dates open questions follow-up actions                                                                                   Meeting notes                                                   Capture decisions, owners, dates, open questions, and follow-up actions.                                                                                                                        project plan list goal milestones owners risks next checkpoint                                                                                                  Project plan                                                    List the goal, milestones, owners, risks, and the next checkpoint.                                                                                                                              decision memo state recommendation alternatives considered evidence risks owner                                                                                 Decision memo                                                   State the recommendation, alternatives considered, evidence, risks, and owner.                                                                                                                  